# Deployment — tv.bakeandgrill.mv

After every `git push`, always provide the cPanel pull & deploy instructions:

## After Every Push

1. **If frontend files changed** (`client/src/**`), build first locally:
```bash
cd /Users/vigani/Website/tv/client && npm run build
cd .. && git add client/dist/ && git commit -m "build: rebuild frontend dist" && git push origin main
```

2. **Pull on cPanel server:**
```bash
cd ~/tv.bakeandgrill.mv
GIT_SSH_COMMAND="ssh -i ~/.ssh/id_ed25519 -o IdentitiesOnly=yes" git pull origin main
```

3. **Restart:** cPanel → Setup Node.js App → RESTART

4. **Verify:**
```bash
curl https://tv.bakeandgrill.mv/api/health
```

## Key Info
- **Server path:** `~/tv.bakeandgrill.mv`
- **SSH key:** `~/.ssh/id_ed25519`
- **GitHub repo:** `git@github.com:ampilarey/tv.bakeandgrill.mv.git`
- **Node app root:** `tv.bakeandgrill.mv/server`
- **Startup file:** `server.js`
- **Always build `client/dist` locally** — server has memory limits
